{"tid":2308913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國會報告狂轟惡法 建議「為擔心受迫害港人掃除取得美國簽證障礙」","createTime":"2020-12-02T08:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T05:00:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"603ce4defc4d5f5dc31279565b7408a2bcb5d2e7","tid":2308913,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"美中經濟與安全審議委員會（USCC）周二發表年度報告，指中共在香港強推國安法，顯示中共對任何反對迹象都不能容忍，亦無意兌現國際承諾。報告建議美國政府為擔心受政治迫害的港人，掃除取得美國簽證的障礙，建議國會研究立法，向在97年後出生的港人給予政治庇護。又指示美國貿易代表在90日內提交報告，評估大陸利用香港逃避或規避貿易法的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201202/SGCRBSEZTBHALDZSYMVHCIH3AM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201202%2FSGCRBSEZTBHALDZSYMVHCIH3AM%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=cc790259\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201202%2FSGCRBSEZTBHALDZSYMVHCIH3AM%2F&h=0180f76a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201202/SGCRBSEZTBHALDZSYMVHCIH3AM/</a>"},{"pid":"d287aa6a305823b7dfca4907d6d90a3a5191b4db","tid":2308913,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T22:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654a80e4f5267ad5279109ecdb4a80ad5111fc07","tid":2308913,"uid":39812,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T22:52:36.000Z","msg":"終於可以移民密西西比州同班侵粉同聲同氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f97b8f7faa39a12f507b7515921b5600790efb","tid":2308913,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T23:26:26.000Z","msg":"禾系腥港人 禾刀要脾護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dee4eeddc6f8a180c9673e66ae27